Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=Doctrine and Method
  - 300
By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
To get a crop one must needs sow the grain with the husk on. ... So
rites and ceremonies are necessary for the growth and perpetuation of
a religion. They are the receptacles that contain the kernel of truth,
and consequently every man must perform them before he reaches the
central truth.
